capital investment period, as defined in subdivision (b)(2)(A), must be filed prior
to October 1, 2019.
(2) An application with the department of revenue for the exemption on
qualified building materials, as defined in subdivision (b)(1)(B), for a qualified
capital investment period, as defined in subdivision (b)(2)(B), must be filed prior
to October 1, 2026.
SECTION 3. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
